  <text>
    <body>
      <div>
        <p><seg type="diplomatic" subtype="address"><seg type="diplomatic" subtype="intitulatio">Edgar king of the Scots</seg> <seg type="diplomatic" subtype="salutation">sends greeting</seg> to all in his kingdom, Scots and English.</seg> <seg type="diplomatic" subtype="disposition"><seg type="diplomatic" subtype="notification">Know that</seg> I concede and donate Paxton to my master Saint Cuthbert and to his monks, just
                     as I had it, with men, lands and waters; <seg type="diplomatic" subtype="holding">and the monks should possess it as freely and quitly as Coldingham, according to
                     their own desire</seg>.</seg> <seg type="diplomatic" subtype="salutation">Farewell.</seg></p>
      </div>
    </body>
  </text>
